**Hexed Wolf** | Werewolf Investigative | Haunted
__Basics__
The Hexed Wolf may learn the roles of those who lynched them and send that info back to the wolfpack.
__Details__
Everyone who lynches a Hexed Wolf will be hexed. During the night, while the Hexed Wolf is a ghost, they may investigate a hexed player to learn their role. This is affected by weak disguises.
The Hexed Wolf may send the identity of a hexed player to wolfpack. The Hexed Wolf investigates the player, but receives no result; the wolfpack will learn both the player and the role.
Both of the Hexed Wolf's investigations are immediate abilities, but it must conduct its first investigation to unlock its second.
The Hexed Wolf is a member of the wolfpack and a lycan.

__Simplified__
Everyone who lynches a Hexed Wolf will be hexed. While the Hexed Wolf is a ghost, at night it may investigate a hexed player to learn their role.
The Hexed Wolf may send the identity of a hexed player to wolfpack. The wolfpack will learn both the player and the role they were investigated as.

__Formalized__
Haunted Role
Inherit: `Pack Lycan`

__Card__
Your identity may be forfeit if you lynch a Hexed Wolf.
